snippet.title: Projapati Song | Projapati 2 | Mithun C | Dev | Jeet Gannguli | Avijit Senn | ‚Ä™Bengal Talkies
snippet.description:
Presenting the official video of the ‚ÄúProjpati ‚Äù title track from the much-awaited film Projapati 2.
‚ÄúProjapati Song‚Äù is a high-octane Bengali wedding dance anthem packed with celebration, colour, and unstoppable energy. Composed in a Jeet-Ganguly‚Äìstyle festive dance beat.

The lyrics carry the fun, poetic, and rhythmic flavour you‚Äôd expect from a Priyo-Chattopadhyay‚Äìinspired wedding track‚Äîfull of joy, jokes, and pure celebration. Featuring the dynamic screen presence of Dev‚Äôs youthful energy and Mithun Chakraborty‚Äôs iconic swag, the track feels like a grand family celebration turned into a dance explosion.

snippet.title: PMGC: THE INDIA CHAPTER | BEFORE THE GAUNTLET
snippet.description:
Every journey to greatness begins with preparation, and in this first episode, Before the Gauntlet, we go behind the scenes with our iQOO Orangutan players as they gear up for PMGC. 

From their performances in BMIC to the countless hours of practice, strategy sessions, and teamwork, this episode captures the dedication and determination that drives Team India. See the players push their limits, overcome challenges, and sharpen their skills, all while building the chemistry and mindset needed to compete on the world stage. 

This is more than just gaming, it‚Äôs the story of ambition, resilience, and the pursuit of glory, giving fans an inside look at what it truly takes to represent India at the highest level of esports.

snippet.title: Super Car Race Motu Patlu Ki Non Stop Comedy Sab Hue Lotpot üòÇ | Motu Patlu | Kiddie Land
snippet.description:
Motu Patlu shamil hote hain ek super car race mein jahan har gadhi car, rocket car aur funny gadget cars unka intezaar kar rahi hoti hain! Motu ki hungry driving aur Patlu ka super tension full-on comedy create kar deti hai. Race ke beech John aur uski gang bhi cheating karne ki koshish karte hain, par Motu Patlu ki masti aur teamwork sabko hila kar rakh deti hai. High-speed stunts, nonstop comedy aur dhamal se bharpur ek zabardast adventure shuru ho jata hai!


Show Name: Motu Patlu
Directed By: Suhas D. Kadav
Written By: Niraj Vikram
Original language: Hindi


#motupatlu  #furfurinagar #kidsanimation

About Motu Patlu:
-----------------------------
Motu and Patlu, two best friends living in the bustling town of Furfuri Nagar, often find themselves in hilarious and troublesome situations. Motu loves eating samosas, which give him bursts of energy, while Patlu is the smarter and slimmer friend who tries to keep Motu out of trouble. Despite their constant troubles, they are usually saved by luck and the help of their good friends like Ghasita Ram, the ever-experienced but often unhelpful companion; Inspector Chingam, the proud but sometimes clumsy police officer; and Dr. Jhatka, the eccentric scientist whose inventions often create more chaos than solutions. Together, they make Furfuri Nagar a lively and fun-filled place full of adventure and laughter.

Race ke beech John aur uski gang bhi cheating karne ki koshish karte hain, par Motu Patlu ki masti aur teamwork sabko hila kar rakh deti hai. High-speed stunts, nonstop comedy aur dhamal se bharpur ek zabardast adventure shuru ho jata hai!


Show Name: Motu Patlu
Directed By: Suhas D. Kadav
Written By: Niraj Vikram
Original language: Hindi


#motupatlu  #furfurinagar #kidsanimation

About Motu Patlu:
-----------------------------
Motu and Patlu, two best friends living in the bustling town of Furfuri Nagar, often find themselves in hilarious and troublesome situations. Motu loves eating samosas, which give him bursts of energy, while Patlu is the smarter and slimmer friend who tries to keep Motu out of trouble. Despite their constant troubles, they are usually saved by luck and the help of their good friends like Ghasita Ram, the ever-experienced but often unhelpful companion; Inspector Chingam, the proud but sometimes clumsy police officer; and Dr. Jhatka, the eccentric scientist whose inventions often create more chaos than solutions. Together, they make Furfuri Nagar a lively and fun-filled place full of adventure and laughter.
